OL,4,Cmoney to tackle SEND 'crisis'
OL,6,FSomerset Council has called on the
OL,7,Fgovernment to change the law or
OL,8,Fincrease funding to help local
OL,9,Fauthorities better support children
OL,10,Fwith special educational needs (SEND).
OL,12,FIt comes amid a warning from the Local
OL,13,FGovernment Association (LGA) that the
OL,14,Fsystem is "failing" and in "urgent
OL,15,Fneed of reform".
