OL,4,Cmoney to tackle SEND 'crisis'
OL,6,FCouncillor Heather Shearer, cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for children, families and
OL,8,Feducation at Somerset Council, said:
OL,9,F"It will take a long time to change
OL,10,Flegislation but they have to look at
OL,11,Fwhat they can do - either small fixes
OL,12,Fin the short-term or give us the
OL,13,Ffunding that actually goes with these
OL,14,Fservices we're trying to provide."
OL,16,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,17,Fsays she is "determined to rebuild
OL,18,Ffamilies' confidence in a system so
OL,19,Fmany rely on".
