OL,6,FA report published by the National
OL,7,FAudit Office (NAO) has warned the SEND
OL,8,Fsystem is "financially unsustainable"
OL,9,Fand "in urgent need of reform".
OL,11,FCouncillor Arooj Shah, chair of the
OL,12,Flocal government association's
OL,13,Fchildren and young people board, said:
OL,14,F"This report is yet another indictment
OL,15,Fof a failing SEND system that is not
OL,16,Fmeeting the care and support needs of
OL,17,Fchildren with special needs."
OL,19,FCllr Shah said he is concerned many
OL,20,Fcouncils will face a "financial cliff-
OL,21,Fedge" if the system is not reformed.
