OL,4,Cmoney to tackle SEND 'crisis'
OL,6,FHe added: "In next week's budget, we
OL,7,Fare hoping that the government will
OL,8,Fset out how it will reform and
OL,9,Fadequately fund the SEND system, so
OL,10,Fchildren get the support they
OL,11,Fdesperately need."
OL,13,FCllr Shearer said many children in
OL,14,FSomerset with special educational
OL,15,Fneeds are either without a school
OL,16,Fplace or have been assigned a place
OL,17,Ftheir family feels is not right for
OL,18,Fthem.
