OL,6,FShe said this has left many parents
OL,7,Fand teachers feeling "quite
OL,8,Fbeleaguered".
OL,10,F"They can see what they need, but
OL,11,Fthey're running at full pace all the
OL,12,Ftime and, whatever government, they
OL,13,Ffeel they're not being supported," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FCllr Shearer has called on the
OL,17,Fgovernment to provide further support
OL,18,Fto local authorities, and said the
OL,19,Fcouncil is doing all it can to tackle
OL,20,Fthe issue in the short-term.
