OL,6,FShe added: "We'll call on the
OL,7,Fgovernment to support us but we also
OL,8,Fhave to do the things that are free or
OL,9,Fcheaper - that is if we can keep our
OL,10,Farms around our own employees and
OL,11,Fensure that they communicate well,
OL,12,Fthey build all those relationships
OL,13,Fwith parents - that should make, at
OL,14,Fleast, a small difference."
OL,16,F"We have to keep our children in the
OL,17,Ffront of our minds. They've only got
OL,18,Fone chance at an education and we have
OL,19,Fto help," she added.
