OL,6,FThe Education Secretary said: "The
OL,7,FNAO's report exposes a system that has
OL,8,Fbeen neglected to the point of crisis,
OL,9,Fwith children and families with SEND
OL,10,Fquite simply being failed on every
OL,11,Fmeasure.
OL,13,F"There will be no more sticking
OL,14,Fplaster politics and short-termism
OL,15,Fwhen it comes to the life chances of
OL,16,Fsome of our most vulnerable children.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
